  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <h1>Measured Building Surveys &amp; Floorplans</h1>
      <p>
        Accurate, professional property measurement and floorplans for renovations, extensions, and documentation.
      </p>
      <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry.html">Request a Survey</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-detail">
    <div class="box-container">
      <h2>Our Measured Survey Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>2D Floorplans:</strong>
          Clear, precise layouts of property interiors—ideal for renovation planning, property marketing, or lease agreements.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Elevations &amp; Sections:</strong>
          Accurate external and internal views supporting detailed planning applications or structural assessments.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Site Plans:</strong>
          Detailed property and boundary measurements crucial for development, planning permissions, and records.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who Benefits from Our Surveys</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Homeowners:</strong>
          Essential for accurate planning of extensions, renovations, or interior design.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Landlords:</strong>
          Clear, professional floorplans to document layouts, assist with lease agreements, and property management.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Property Investors:</strong>
          Precise measurements to evaluate opportunities, assess alterations, and make informed decisions.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Choose LEM Building Surveying?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Tailored Service:</strong>
          Personalised survey solutions matching your property's unique characteristics and project goals.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Local Expertise:</strong>
          Familiarity with regional building types, layouts, and planning requirements across the North West.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Clear Deliverables:</strong>
          Professionally presented, easy-to-understand plans and reports that communicate key information clearly.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-areas improved-areas">
    <div class="box-container">
      <div class="areas-header">
        <h2>Areas We Cover</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Based in Connah’s Quay, we serve property owners across Flintshire, Chester, and surrounding areas
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="areas-content">
        <div class="dropdown-card">
          <label class="dropdown-label" for="areaDropdown">Jump to an area:</label>
          <div class="custom-select">
            <select id="areaDropdown" data-area-select>
              <option value="">Select an area…</option>
              <option value="/connahs-quay.html">Connah’s Quay</option>
